{"tid":1177570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍首長控中國違背對南海承諾 籲各國集體行動","createTime":"2019-05-29T23:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T23:21:40.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b180943ebcd7dd676ba7a25562b50605cc1137c7","tid":1177570,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:11:29.000Z","msg":"美國軍方參謀首長聯席會議主席鄧福德將軍今天表示，中國國家主席習近平曾承諾不會將南海島礁軍事化卻食言，他呼籲各國採取「集體行動」要北京負起責任。<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德（Joseph Dunford）說，他不是號召採取軍事行動，但強調必須執行國際法。<br />\n<br />\n他在布魯金斯研究所（Brookings Institution）舉行的一項美國安全與國防會議表示：「2016年秋天，習近平主席曾向歐巴馬總統承諾，他們不會將那些島礁軍事化。結果我們今天看到1萬呎長的跑道、彈藥貯存設施以及常規部署的飛彈防禦能力和航空能力。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德說：「因此他們顯然違背了那項承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n他強調：「我不是建議要作軍事反應。必須要做的是針對違反國際規範和準則者一致採取集體行動。必須要設法讓他們負起責任，以嚇阻未來再犯。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2806447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2806447&d=5SGopU86zwsNpZ2NEmuics2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=0034e027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2806447&h=095b1165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2806447</a>"},{"pid":"a83aed90334dc6272f0b154c8d7c1b4747a396d7","tid":1177570,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:13:41.000Z","msg":"快 炸撚左個島佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家時機成熟 開得維尼波了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d54dd06bd2f60623060626c7aae5158048f8f5f","tid":1177570,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T23:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁講即係下一步就炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87aba45ce170b33eaa445496e35607ed1ee882f2","tid":1177570,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":